<div align="center"><b>Mp3Fixer Script for amaroK</b></div>

<p>
<b>About:</b><br>
Mp3Fixer is a script for fixing VBR encoded mp3 files, which display a bogus track length in your
audio player. Mp3Fixer calculates the real track length and adds the missing XING
header to the file.
</p>

<p>
<b>Usage:</b><br>
Select a track in the playlist, then start Mp3Fixer from the context-menu (right mouse click).
</p>

